arts.ttl: Europa League: Talents lead AZ to victory over Fenerbahce
arts.sum: AZ Alkmaar secured a 3-1 victory over Jose Mourinho’s Fenerbahce on Thursday evening. Maarten Martens handed first European starts to winger Jayden Addai and midfielder Dave Kwakman due to an injury crisis at the club. arts.ttl: Manchester United Academy Briefing: Adam Lawrence discusses UEFA Youth League, Sekou Kone and AZ Alkmaar
arts.sum: “In the away leg we conceded two goals late on which was disappointing so it was good the boys had that bit about them later on in the game to manage it right and properly and not give them any opportunities, so that was pleasing. And the boys have done well over the two games and deserve the opportunity in the next round, so we look forward to it.”
